quotes.message: Today is a good day to remember you are one out of one, there's no need to be like anyone else when no one can ever be like you.
You have to change the "what if's" to "when" because it's not about whether you can, it's just a matter of time.
As time goes by it becomes increasingly more difficult to remember the place or activity, but the one thing I'll never forget is what you made me feel... and maybe that's all that really matters.
You can't control what happens today, but you can control how you let it affect you and your energy, stay in control and keep going. You can still decide what kind of day you want to have.
Even if things don't work out the way you imagined, you'll be proud of the fact that you even tried, because most people are too scared to even try... but you're not most people
